verbose_text: Cells were cultured in MCDB-131 medium (Sigma-Aldrich, St. Louis, MO), supplemented with 10% heat inactivated fetal bovine serum (FBS) (HyClone-GE Healthcare Life Sciences, Logan, UT) and endothelial growth factors (EGM-2 SingleQuots supplement, omitting FBS, hydrocortisone and gentamicin; Clonetics-Lonza, Walkersville, MD) at 37 degreesC and 5% CO 2 in air, and used at passage 1 or 2.
